org.sbml.squeezer.io
Class SBFileFilter

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.filechooser.FileFilter
      org.sbml.squeezer.io.SBFileFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
FileFilter
public class SBFileFilter
extends FileFilter
implements FileFilter

A file filter implementation for TeX and text files. It also accepts directories. Otherwise one could not browse in the file system.

Since:
1.0
Version:
Author:
Andreas Dräger
